m <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Robert fitzRandulph de Trafford was born about 1152, in Trafford Manor, Lancashire, England as the son of Randulph de Trafford. He married Christian de Chetham in 1176, in Lancaster, Lancashire, England. He died about 1204, in his hometown, at the age of 54."},"et":{"about 1152–about 1204":"umbes 1152–umbes 1204","1152–1204":"1152–1204","1158–Female":"1158–Surnud","1156–Female":"1156–Surnud","1180–1221":"1180–1221","1182–1220":"1182–1220","1184–1260":"1184–1260","1187–Male":"1187–Surnud","1124–Male":"1124–Surnud","about 1184":"umbes 1184","about 1180":"umbes 1180","1176":"1176","1187":"1187","1220":"1220","1152":"1152","1184":"1184","1260":"1260","1182":"1182","1180":"1180","1204":"1204","1158":"1158","1179":"1179","1124":"1124","about 1204":"umbes 1204","1156":"1156","1221":"1221","about 1187":"umbes 1187","about 1152":"umbes 1152","Lancaster, Lancashire, England":"Lancaster, Lancashire, England","Trafford, Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, England","Trafford Manor, Lancashire, England":"Trafford Manor, Lancashire, England","Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, England"},"fi":{"about 1152–about 1204":"noin 1152–noin 1204","1152–1204":"1152–1204","1158–Female":"1158–Kuollut","1156–Female":"1156–Kuollut","1180–1221":"1180–1221","1182–1220":"1182–1220","1184–1260":"1184–1260","1187–Male":"1187–Kuollut","1124–Male":"1124–Kuollut","about 1184":"noin 1184","about 1180":"noin 1180","1176":"1176","1187":"1187","1220":"1220","1152":"1152","1184":"1184","1260":"1260","1182":"1182","1180":"1180","1204":"1204","1158":"1158","1179":"1179","1124":"1124","about 1204":"noin 1204","1156":"1156","1221":"1221","about 1187":"noin 1187","about 1152":"noin 1152","Lancaster, Lancashire, England":"Lancaster, Lancashire, England","Trafford, Lancashire, England":"Lancashire, England","Trafford Manor, Lancas